import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { View, Text, Image,StyleSheet,TextInput,Button,TouchableOpacity} from 'react-native'
import PetScreen from './PetScreen'
 
 
const PetDetails =()=>{
    return (
 
        <View style={{backgroundColor:'grey',padding:'30px'}}>
        <Image 
                 style={{ width: '250px', height: '120px' ,alignItems:'center',justifyContent:'center',marginLeft:"70px",marginBottom:"10px"}}
                 
                 source = {{uri:'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcShTurouxhjqO7a7i3DiIo4lxlBcWSQ7L4QFQ&usqp=CAU'}}
               />
                   <Text>
                    Pet Name : Kitty
                   </Text>
                   <Text>
                     Pet DOB :Thus Jun 1 2017
                   </Text>
                   <Text>
                    Pet Location :  Chennai
                   </Text>
                   <Text>
                    Pet Breed : Munchkin
                   </Text>
                  <Text>Owner Details :</Text>
                  
                <Text style={{
                   padding:20,
                   height:100,
                   width:250,
                   margin:10,
                   borderWidth:1,
                   backgroundColor:'#fff'
                }}>
                  Owner details
                </Text>
                <View style={{flexDirection:"row"}}>
                <Text>Album</Text>
                <Image source = {{uri:'https://www.pngitem.com/pimgs/m/33-330111_album-icon-png-transparent-png.png'}} style={{width: 30, height: 30,marginLeft:"196px" }} />
                </View>
                <View style={{flexDirection:"row"}}>
                <Text style={{marginTop:"6px" }}>Schedule</Text>
                <Image source = {{uri:'https://i.pinimg.com/originals/9c/62/4d/9c624d04a5228a3f8be626705da87e64.png'}} style={{width: 30, height: 30,marginLeft:"100px" }} />
                <Image source = {{uri:'https://image.freepik.com/free-icon/view-details_318-1493.jpg'}} style={{width: 30, height: 30,marginLeft:"50px", marginBottom:"20px"}} />
</View>
             <View style={{flexDirection:"row"}}>
             <TouchableOpacity style={styles.button} >
                <Text>Call</Text>
             </TouchableOpacity>   
             
             <TouchableOpacity style={styles.button} >
                <Text>Delete</Text>
             </TouchableOpacity>
                </View>
                </View>
             )
          }
       
        
       
       const styles = StyleSheet.create({
          container: {
         
            color:'red',
          
          },
          button: {
             alignItems: "center",
             backgroundColor: "#fff",
            marginLeft:30,
             padding: 10
           }})
           export default PetDetails
